      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REALITY UTE (4) is a promising dog in the frame at three of eight starts including three wins and was in the minors again latest (29.72) over 515m at this track. Tends to go well on this box draw. Has the ability and looks a key chance this line-up. FROMELLES POPPY (1) had some strong recent form but was below best last time when eighth (31.24) in a Restricted WIN at Ballarat. Normally fast to begin but shuffled back last time. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Cannot be taken lightly. DR. HOPPER (2) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by half a length at Sale in a handy 24.78 beating Akina Sari. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. SILVER MACK (3) profiles nicely over this trip.",
